OL,7,FChippenham MP and Science Sec Michelle
OL,8,FDonelan insists she has been
OL,9,F'transparent' about the cost to the
OL,10,Ftaxpayer of her libel fees
OL,12,FChippenham MP Michelle Donelan insists
OL,13,Fshe has been "very transparent" after
OL,14,Fit surfaced that taxpayers have paid
OL,15,Fout to cover costs of a libel case
OL,16,Fagainst her.
