OL,3,CChippenham MP: 'We have been
OL,4,Ctransparent' over #34k taxpayer libel
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FThe Guardian reported on Thursday that
OL,8,Fthe cost of the Science Secretary's
OL,9,Flegal fees were more than double the
OL,10,Foriginal sum the government had
OL,11,Fadmitted to.
OL,13,FThe Department for Science, Innovation
OL,14,Fand Technology confirmed last month
OL,15,Fthat it paid #15,000 to settle libel
OL,16,Faction brought by Professor Kate Sang,
OL,17,Fafter Ms Donelan wrongly accused her
OL,18,Fof supporting or expressing sympathy
OL,19,Ffor Hamas.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
