OL,3,CChippenham MP: 'We have been
OL,4,Ctransparent' over #34k taxpayer libel
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FHowever, it has since been revealed
OL,8,Fthat an additional #19,000 of
OL,9,Ftaxpayers' money was used to cover the
OL,10,Flegal costs.
OL,12,FSpeaking on a visit to Melksham on
OL,13,FFriday, Ms Donelan told ITV West
OL,14,FCountry there has been "no increase"
OL,15,Fin costs and her department has been
OL,16,F"very transparent".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
