OL,3,CChippenham MP: 'We have been
OL,4,Ctransparent' over #34k taxpayer libel
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,F"There's no increase. There was a
OL,8,Flibel settlement, obviously lawyers
OL,9,Fwere involved in the libel settlement,
OL,10,Fthat was always going to be the case,"
OL,11,FMs Donelan said.
OL,13,F"Post that, the external council fee
OL,14,Fhas been submitted, which we have been
OL,15,Fvery transparent about again, and then
OL,16,Fthere was a notional cost for internal
OL,17,Fgovernment services."
