OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FIn a letter to Labour's shadow science
OL,8,Fsecretary Peter Kyle, the Science
OL,9,FDepartment's permanent secretary Sarah
OL,10,FMunby admitted the full cost was more
OL,11,Fthan twice the figure the department
OL,12,Fhad admitted to, with another #19,385
OL,13,Fspent on legal costs.
OL,15,FMs Munby said the taxpayer had covered
OL,16,Fthe costs as ministers were
OL,17,Findemnified for "things done or
OL,18,Fdecisions made in the course of their
OL,19,Fministerial duties".
