OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FThe figure includes #7,785 of costs
OL,8,Fincurred by the Government Legal
OL,9,FDepartment and another #11,600 spent
OL,10,Fon external counsel, with neither
OL,11,Ffigure including VAT.
OL,13,FOpposition figures have called for Ms
OL,14,FDonelan, who will contest the new
OL,15,FMelksham & Devizes seat at the next
OL,16,Fgeneral election, to pay back the
OL,17,Fmoney herself.
