OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FMr Kyle said the fact taxpayers were
OL,8,Fpicking up the bill was "a slap in the
OL,9,Fface to hardworking families", adding
OL,10,Fthe money had been "wasted on
OL,11,Funprofessional and libelous behaviour
OL,12,Ffrom a Conservative cabinet minister".
OL,14,FLiberal Democrat deputy leader Daisy
OL,15,FCooper said: "People's taxes should
OL,16,Fnot be used to bail out disgraced
OL,17,FConservative ministers. This saga
OL,18,Fstinks of a rotten cover-up, with
OL,19,FDonelan at its core."
