OL,7,FProf Sang after Ms Donelan tweeted she
OL,8,Fhad written to UKRI in October,
OL,9,Fexpressing "disgust and outrage" that
OL,10,FProf Sang and another academic, Dr
OL,11,FKamna Patel, had "shared extremist
OL,12,Fviews" and, in Prof Sang's case,
OL,13,Fexpressed sympathy for Hamas after the
OL,14,FOctober 7 attacks in Israel.
