OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FThe letter followed a tweet by Prof
OL,8,FSang saying "This is disturbing", and
OL,9,Fcontaining a link to an article by the
OL,10,FGuardian newspaper describing the
OL,11,Fresponse to the Hamas attacks in the
OL,12,FUK, while Dr Patel had retweeted a
OL,13,Fpost describing Israeli actions as
OL,14,F"genocide and apartheid".
OL,16,FMs Donelan's intervention triggered an
OL,17,Finvestigation by UKRI, which had
OL,18,Fappointed the academics to its
OL,19,Fadvisory group on equality, diversity
OL,20,Fand inclusion (EDI).
