OL,7,FDetails obtained under freedom of
OL,8,Finformation rules by website Research
OL,9,FProfessional News found the UKRI
OL,10,Finvestigation had cost #23,280,
OL,11,Fincluding VAT, putting the total cost
OL,12,Fto the taxpayer of Ms Donelan's letter
OL,13,Fat almost #60,000.
OL,15,FLast month, Ms Donelan accepted that
OL,16,FProf Sang's comments referred to the
OL,17,FGuardian story as a whole, and not
OL,18,Fjust the headline, which focused on
OL,19,Fthe government's crackdown on support
OL,20,Ffor Hamas.
