OL,8,Fevidence" the academic was a supporter
OL,9,Fof Hamas.
OL,11,FThe Department for Science, Innovation
OL,12,Fand Technology said: "In line with the
OL,13,Festablished practice under multiple
OL,14,Fadministrations of all political
OL,15,Fcolours, Ministers are provided with
OL,16,Flegal support and representation where
OL,17,Fmatters relate to their conduct and
OL,18,Fresponsibilities as a Minister."
